abstract: Arizona Cardinals sign offensive tackle D J Humphries to four-year contract; other football news noted.
lead_paragraph: The team agreed to a four-year-contract with Florida offensive tackle D.J. Humphries, the 24th overall pick in the N.F.L. draft.

headline.print_headline: Cardinals Sign Top Pick to a Four-Year Contract
